    <title>"Handover Key Management and Re-authentication Problem Statement", Charles  Clancy</title>
    <link>http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-clancy-hokey-reauth-ps-01.txt</link>
    <description>This document describes the Handover Keying (HOKEY) problem statement. The current EAP keying framework is not designed to support re-authentication and handovers. This often cause unacceptable latency in various mobile wireless environments. HOKEY plans to address these HOKEY plans to address these problems by implementing a generic mechanism to reuse derived EAP keying material for hand-off.</description>
